    <body>
        <h1>Log4cxx Support</h1>
                        <p>
       log4cxx user support is provided via the log4cxx-user@logging.apache.org mailing list.
       Please search mailing list archives and <a href="http://nagoya.apache.org/jira/secure/BrowseProject.jspa?id=10550">bug tracker</a> before posting.
       The development mailing lists are described in the <a href="contributing.html">contributing</a> topic.
                         </p>

                        <h3>Mailing List Archives</h3>
                                <p>
                    log4cxx-user@logging.apache.org is archived at                                                    
                    <a href="http://marc.theaimsgroup.com/?l=log4cxx-user&amp;r=1&amp;w=2">MARC</a>, 
                    <a href="http://dir.gmane.org/gmane.comp.apache.logging.log4cxx.user">GMANE</a>,
                    and apache.org (<a href="http://mail-archives.eu.apache.org/mod_mbox/logging-log4cxx-user/">mod_mbox</a>,
                    <a href="http://nagoya.apache.org/eyebrowse/SummarizeList?listId=219">eyebrowse</a>).</p>

                        <h3>Subscribe</h3>
                                <p>
                                Subscribe to either the list or to the digest list:
                                </p>

                                <ul>
                                        <li>
                                        <p>
                                        To subscribe to this list send an e-mail to <br/>
                                        <a href="mailto:log4cxx-user-subscribe@logging.apache.org">
                                        log4cxx-user-subscribe@logging.apache.org</a>.
                                        </p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                        <p>
                                        To subscribe to the digest list sent an e-mail to <br />
                                        <a href="mailto:log4cxx-user-digest-subscribe@logging.apache.org">
                                        log4cxx-user-digest-subscribe@logging.apache.org</a>.
                                        </p>
                                        </li>
                                </ul>

                        <h3>Unsubscribe</h3>
                                <p>
                                To unsubscribe send an email to the relevant email address:
                                </p>

                                <ul>
                                        <li>
                                        <p>
                                        To unsubscribe from this list send an e-mail to <br/>
                                        <a href="mailto:log4cxx-user-unsubscribe@logging.apache.org">
                                        log4cxx-user-unsubscribe@logging.apache.org</a>.
                                        </p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                        <p>
                                        To unsubscribe from the digest list sent an e-mail to <br/>
                                        <a href="mailto:log4cxx-user-digest-unsubscribe@logging.apache.org">
                                        log4cxx-user-digest-unsubscribe@logging.apache.org</a>.
                                        </p>
                                        </li>
                                </ul>

                        <h3>Posting</h3>
                                <p>
                                        Please have a quick read through the <a
                                        href="http://jakarta.apache.org/site/mail.html">
                                        guidelines</a>, thanks.
                                </p>

                                <p>
                                        <strong>To prevent spam, we require you to be subscribed to
                                        the list before posting to it.</strong>
                                </p>

                                <p>
                                        Post a message to the list by sending mail to
                                        <a href="mailto:log4cxx-user@logging.apache.org">
                                        log4cxx-user@logging.apache.org</a>.  Message containing attachments are
                                        not accepted.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                        To check for known bugs, report new ones or submit a patch, use the <a href="http://nagoya.apache.org/jira/secure/BrowseProject.jspa?id=10550">log4cxx bug tracker</a>.
                                </p>
        </body>
